ellen">Joan Mellen</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/christina-newland">Christina Newland</a></dt><dd>UK/USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/jugoslav-pantelic">Jugoslav Pantelić</a></dt><dd>Serbia</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/nenad-polimac">Nenad Polimac</a></dt><dd>Croatia</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/caitlin-quinlan">Caitlin Quinlan</a></dt><dd>UK</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/mayukh-sen">Mayukh Sen</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/david-thompson">David Thompson</a></dt><dd>UK</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/marjan-vujovic">Marjan Vujovic</a></dt><dd>Serbia</dd></dl></section><section><h3>Directors</h3><dl><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/carlos-abascal-peiro">Carlos Abascal Peiró</a></dt><dd>Spain</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/lorcan-finnegan">Lorcan Finnegan</a></dt><dd>Ireland</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/karyn-kusama">Karyn Kusama</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/stanley-kwan">Stanley Kwan</a></dt><dd>Hong Kong</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/brett-morgen">Brett Morgen</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/phyllis-nagy">Phyllis Nagy</a></dt><dd>US</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/paul-schrader">Paul Schrader</a></dt><dd>US</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/malgorzata-szumowska">Małgorzata Szumowska</a></dt><dd>Poland</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/ann-turner">Ann Turner</a></dt><dd>Australia</dd></dl></section></div></de